    "Listing 2: Prompts used in STORM (continue), corresponding to Line 24, 31, 32 in Algorithm 1.Algorithm 1: STORM Input:Topic t, maximum perspective N, maximum conversation round M Output:Outline O, references R 1 P0 = \"basic fact writer...\" // Constant.",
